#! python3
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from pandas.tseries.offsets import *
import tushare as ts
from pandas import  DataFrame,Series
import os
import multiprocessing
import multiprocessing.pool

def calc(code):
    '''
        根据code 计算7年内各年内涨跌
    :return:
    '''

    print('开始计算code:{0}..'.format(code))
    #根据code拉取七年内的行情数据
    data = ts.get_k_data(code,'2006-12-29','2017-12-31')
    if data is None or len(data) <=0:
        return

    #取得收盘价,并以日期建立索引
    work_day_close_data = Series(data= data.close.values, index= map(pd.to_datetime, data.date.values))
    #补齐非工作日，缺失数据用前值填补
    close_data = work_day_close_data.reindex(pd.date_range(start='2006-12-29',end='2017-12-31',freq='D'),method='Pad')
    for year in range(2007,2018):
        #前半年
        front = close_data[pd.datetime(year,1,1):pd.datetime(year,6,30)]
        #后半年
        back = Series(close_data[pd.datetime(year,7,1):pd.datetime(year,12,31)].values[:len(front.index.values)], index=front.index.values)
        #计算涨跌
        zd = back.div(front)-1
        #筛选出 大于200% 的
        result = zd[zd > 2]
        if len(result) > 0:
            # 生成code 列
            codes = {'code':[code for c in range(len(zd))],'zd':zd.values}
            # 生成表格数据
            frame = DataFrame.from_dict(codes)
            frame.index.names=['rownum']
            frame.to_csv('./zdf/{0}.csv'.format(code),columns=['code','zd'],header=True)
    print('完成计算code:{0}..'.format(code))

def run(codes):
    try:
        os.chdir('.')
        if not os.path.exists('./zdf'):
            os.mkdir('./zdf')
        groups = np.reshape(codes, (12, 300))
        pool = multiprocessing.pool.Pool(12)
        for g in groups:
            for code in g:
                pool.apply_async(calc, (code))
        pool.close()
        pool.join()
        print('全部计算完成.')
    except Exception as e:
        print(e)
